Package: telegramchatbot
Type: Package
Title: What the Package Does (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin Barner
Maintainer: Martin Barner <m@martinbarner.de>
Description: Framework to set up a simple Telegram Chatbot. Build a chatbot in three steps: 1. Create all "answers" that the bot knows 2. Link them with buttons and commands 3. Start the bot. This can be combined with more complex features in the telegram.bot package.
